  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You&rsquo;ve sat on your favorite barstool at the Rusty Dragon every night for as long as you can remember&mdash; and some nights you can&rsquo;t remember thanks to a few too many drinks. In your various hazes, you&rsquo;ve gotten to know the tap house&rsquo;s proprietor, Ameiko, or one of her regulars, Sandru, quite well. Additionally, you&rsquo;re well acquainted with a variety of uses for strong drink.</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">Any time you have an alcoholic beverage on hand, you can expend one use of it to grant you a +2 trait bonus on a Heal check. This bonus increases to +4 if you&rsquo;re treating your favorite drinking buddy (your NPC of choice).</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">NPC Choices</span></strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">Ameiko, Sandru</span></p>",
